<h1 id="terminology">Terminology</h1>
<p>Each question and answer pair should be represented in a ValueSet. In the ValueSet, the code and the display value should be the unique identifier and title of the element should be capture from the SDC form.</p>

<p>These codes and titles in the ValueSet are mapped to standardized terminologies (e.g. SNOMED-CT) using a ConceptMap Resource. Data extraction and mapping can then be aided through the use of these codes.</p>
